        Creepypasta Files for Android v0.1 <http://hackbytes.com>

This is the master repository of the "Creepypasta Files for Android"
app. The submodule repositories can be found at the following locations:

  http://github.com/byronsanchez/creepypasta-files-resources-android
  http://github.com/byronsanchez/creepypasta-files-dependencies-android

INSTRUCTIONS

  Clone the creepypasta-files-android repository, or alternatively,
  clone your fork of the creepypasta-files-android repository. Then
  add the necessary submodules:

    cd creepypasta-files-android
    git submodule add https://github.com/byronsanchez/creepypasta-files-dependencies-android.git libs
    git submodule add https://github.com/byronsanchez/creepypasta-files-resources-android.git res
    git commit -m 'first commit with submodules'

  Now you're all set to hack "Creepypasta Files for Android"!

STRUCTURE

  The repository tree structure.

    /            - contains the entire "Creepypasta Files for Android"
                   application.

    assets/      - contains files that supplement application
                   functionality (e.g., database schema file).

    libs/        - contains the "Creepypasta Files for Android"
                   dependencies submodule.

    res/         - contains the "Creepypasta Files for Android"
                   resources submodule. This submodule contains
                   image and media assets used in the application.

    src/         - contains the "Creepypasta Files for Android" source
                   code.

